title: Looking for ranked 5 Team. really good support.  also maybe competitive 3's
body: I am a really good support and all around good payer.  i am looking for a good ranked 5 team to play on that is active and serious to enter tournaments.  I do not really solo que ranked.  i prefer duo or teams. any good  ranked team will work for me. also great a 3's. comment on here if you would like me to try out for your team.
